column1: ## Detection Date Note = Detection Date/Time is last detection at an interrogation site as determined by DART.
## Exclusions = Fish tagged as adults as determined by DART are excluded from the TribPit Observations File.
##     This determination is based on a combination of 1. tagging flags 2. length at tagging 3. capture method.
## Source = Columbia River DART. Data Courtesy of Pacific States Marine Fisheries Commission.
